sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Studio/CLI
    participant Net as Network (Socket)
    participant Auth as Auth Manager
    participant Log as System Logger
    participant SysKB as System KB (Master)

    Note over App,SysKB: Luồng Xác thực (Authentication)
    App->>Net: Gửi LOGIN [user] [pass]
    Net->>Auth: Xác thực credentials
    Auth->>SysKB: Query: SELECT * FROM users
    SysKB-->>Auth: Dữ liệu User & Role
    Auth-->>Net: Đăng nhập thành công (RBAC)
    Net-->>App: LOGIN_SUCCESS + SessionId
    
    Note over App,SysKB: Luồng Chẩn đoán (Diagnostics)
    Auth->>Log: LogAudit: "User root logged in"
    Log->>SysKB: INSERT INTO audit_logs IN system
    Log->>Net: Stream log (If subscribed)
    Net-->>App: Hiển thị log Real-time (Console/Dashboard)
